Sentencas: A new spinel oxide CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 (CFLO) has been synthesized as a cathode material for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: CFLO has good structure stability up to 900 degrees C.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the material can survive in both CO2 and steam-containing atmospheres.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared with the Li-free sample, the Li-doping strategy significantly regulates the material's electronic structure.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The low valence of Li leads to the increased amount of Fe and Co cations with higher valences.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, doping Li creates more oxygen vacancies at the material surface, which benefits the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR).
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The improved cathode performance for CFLO has been demonstrated that a cell using CFLO cathode reaches a peak power density of 1052 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell performance is 60% larger than the Li-free cell, and similar results can be detected at other testing temperatures.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the CFLO cell shows good long-term stability in the working condition.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This study proposes the Lidoping strategy to modify spinel oxides and also provides a new spinel oxide as a high-performing cathode for H-SOFCs.
Titulo: A new CoFe1.9Li0.1O4 spinel oxide cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells
